<messaging:emailTemplate subject="PRK-{!RelatedTo.ASI_MFM_PO_Name__c}   {!RelatedTo.ASI_MFM_Supplier_Name__r.name}       PO-{!RelatedTo.Name}   " recipientType="User" relatedToType="ASI_MFM_PO__c"><messaging:htmlEmailBody ><html>    <body>   <table><tr><td>{!RelatedTo.ASI_MFM_Supplier_Name__r.name} </td></tr><tr><td> 안녕하십니까?</td></tr></table>   <table>     <tr><td> 페르노리카코리아 구매팀 입니다.  </td> </tr>                  <tr><td> 첨부한 내용과 같이 구매오더를 보내드리오니  </td> </tr>         <tr><td> 내용이 제출하신 견적과 일치 하는지 꼭 확인하시기 바랍니다.  </td> </tr>               <tr><td> 납품시에는 거래명세표 및 세금 계산서에 PO번호를 적시하여 주시기 바랍니다.   </td> </tr>            <tr><td> 그리고, 전자세금계산서 발행은 첨부파일의 "전자세금계산서 이메일" 주소로 발행하여 주시기 바랍니다.   </td> </tr>         </table><table><tr><td>To Whom It May Concern</td><td></td> </tr><tr><td> This email is to inform you about PO creation from purchasing team of Pernod Ricard Korea.  </td> </tr>  <tr><td> Kindly review the details of PO as attached and confirm if the PO is correctly placed based on your proposed quotation.  </td> </tr>         <tr><td> It is required that you write down PO number on the packing list or tax invoices when you deliver shipment or render services.</td> </tr>   <tr><td> Lastly, please issue an electronic tax invoice to "Electronic Invoice Email address" written in the attached PDF form. </td> </tr>   <tr><td> Thanks.</td></tr>      </table></body></html></messaging:htmlEmailBody>            <messaging:attachment renderAs="PDF"  filename="{!RelatedTo.name}">               <c:ASI_MFM_KR_PO_PDFwAH_Component po_id="{!RelatedTo.Id}" /></messaging:attachment>                    </messaging:emailTemplate>